translate spanish strings:
    old "Clerk"
    new "Кассир"
# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:244
translate spanish hwb_s09_a9237f43:

    # "Clerk" "{alpha=0.1}-{alpha=0.3}c{alpha=0.5}l{alpha=0.7}o{alpha=1.0}sed off, so only the guided tours are open right now.{/alpha}"
    Clerk "{alpha=0.1}-{alpha=0.3}за{alpha=0.5}кры{alpha=0.7}ты{alpha=1.0}, поэтому сейчас открыты только экскурсии.{/alpha}"

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:248
translate spanish hwb_s09_88f7d371:

    # "Marina looks like she’s seen a ghost."
    "Marina parece que ha visto un fantasma."

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:250
translate spanish hwb_s09_52f3484b:

    # Amber "What’s up?"
    Amber "Что такое?"

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:252
translate spanish hwb_s09_3cd7b60d:

    # "I take my wallet from where it’s just sitting forgotten on the counter."
    "Tomo mi cartera de donde está olvidada en el mostrador."

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:254
translate spanish hwb_s09_026a7e50:

    # Marina "Um, I was just asking about the canyon and the tours and stuff."
    Marina "Эм, я просто узнавала о каньоне и о всяких экскурсиях."

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:256
translate spanish hwb_s09_39f0dc87:

    # "The clerk nods."
    "El empleado asiente."

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:258
translate spanish hwb_s09_518b23f7:

    # "Clerk" "Yup, I was saying how if you’re here to sightsee you might have some trouble. A lot of it’s closed off ‘cause of all the kids coming and causing trouble looking for treasure."
    Clerk "Ага, я тут ну типа объясняла, что у вас могут возникнуть всякие там трудности, если хотите поглазеть на достопримечательности. Типа многие экскурсии прикрыли из-за всякой шпаны, которая доставляет неприятности, пытаясь найти сокровище."

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:260
translate spanish hwb_s09_1e9b1839:

    # "Damn. I’m not surprised, but that’s frustrating."
    "Maldición. No me sorprende, pero es frustrante."

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:262
translate spanish hwb_s09_ea134bc8:

    # Amber "What isn’t closed off?"
    Amber "А какие не закрыты?"

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:264
translate spanish hwb_s09_2a9e297e:

    # "Clerk" "Well there are still some tours you can go on. Most of ‘em, I think. But you can’t do the self-guided ones."
    Clerk "Ну есть парочка экскурсий вообще-то. Но вам нельзя на те, которые без гида."

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:268
translate spanish hwb_s09_fc41cf3c:

    # "Marina’s looks at me, eyes wide. Clearly she’s expecting some solution from me."
    "Marina me mira, con los ojos muy abiertos. Claramente espera que yo tenga alguna solución."

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:272
translate spanish hwb_s09_9a3b76ae:

    # "I just smile at the attendant-"
    "Solo le sonrío al dependiente-"

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:274
translate spanish hwb_s09_05e7e96d:

    # Amber "Got it. Thank you!"
    Amber "Понятно. Спасибо!"

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:288
translate spanish hwb_s09_f026b4e0:

    # "-and lead a dumbstruck Marina out of the store."
    "-y saco a una Marina atónita de la tienda."

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:322
translate spanish hwb_s09_18914b30:

    # "As I unlock the RV, Marina prances around me."
    "Mientras abro la casa rodante, Marina brinca a mi alrededor."

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:324
translate spanish hwb_s09_af875778:

    # Marina "What are we gonna do?"
    Marina "Что мы будем делать?"

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:328
translate spanish hwb_s09_73d44e37:

    # Amber "Well, I’m gonna take a nap."
    Amber "Ну, я собираюсь вздремнуть."

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:330
translate spanish hwb_s09_0764ef52:

    # "She stops."
    "Se detiene."

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:334
translate spanish hwb_s09_5b48006b:

    # Marina "Huh?"
    Marina "Аа?"

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:336
translate spanish hwb_s09_ff0ec104:

    # Amber "I’m tired, so I’m going to nap for a little bit. I checked one of the pamphlets and there’s a tour at 6:30, so we’ll just join that and then sneak off."
    Amber "Я устала, так что хочу немного поспать. Я просмотрела один из проспектов и есть экскурсия на 6:30, поэтому мы просто присоединимся к ней и затем улизнем."

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:338
translate spanish hwb_s09_2ced5b97:

    # Marina "Like, on our own?"
    Marina "То есть, сами по себе?"

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:340
translate spanish hwb_s09_c51f294e:

    # Amber "Uh, yeah."
    Amber " Э-э, да."

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:342
translate spanish hwb_s09_a3892fc4:

    # "Her eyes go wide again."
    "Sus ojos se abren de par en par otra vez."

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:346
translate spanish hwb_s09_df89e813:

    # Marina "Amber, you’re a genius!"
    Marina "Эмбер, ты гений!"

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:350
translate spanish hwb_s09_1ca169d7:

    # "I twist a lock of my hair around my finger and glance away. Her constant compliments are a little embarrassing. Especially for stuff that seems obvious to me."
    "Enredo un mechón de mi cabello alrededor de mi dedo y desvío la mirada. Sus cumplidos constantes son un poco vergonzosos. Especialmente por cosas que a mí me parecen obvias."

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:352
translate spanish hwb_s09_5b31eecd:

    # Amber "Thanks. It’s not much of a plan though."
    Amber "Спасибо. Но вообще это не ахти какой план."

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:354
translate spanish hwb_s09_e2b49dc8:

    # Marina "Yeah, but at least it’s a plan! I thought we were gonna have to just give up or something."
    Marina "Да, но, по крайней мере, это план! Я уж думала, мы сдадимся."

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:356
translate spanish hwb_s09_66ead2a9:

    # Amber "Nah. \"Rules are made to be broken\" and all that."
    Amber "Неа. “Правила созданы для того, чтобы их нарушать” и все такое."

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:358
translate spanish hwb_s09_a60a80e2:

    # "I feel a bit guilty that we’ll be breaking rules specifically put in place because of people like us. But I can safely say that we’ll be more careful than the average treasure hunter."
    "Me siento un poco culpable de que vayamos a romper reglas puestas específicamente por gente como nosotras. Pero puedo decir con seguridad que seremos más cuidadosas que el cazador de tesoros promedio."

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:360
translate spanish hwb_s09_17738013:

    # "Just picturing Mariah, I can easily see her smashing down ancient ruins in her search."
    "Solo con imaginar a Mariah, puedo verla fácilmente derribando ruinas antiguas en su búsqueda."

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:364
translate spanish hwb_s09_ebd2c721:

    # Amber "But yeah, wake me up at 5:30, unless you’re going to nap too?"
    Amber "В общем, разбуди меня в 5:30, или ты тоже хочешь вздремнуть?"

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:368
translate spanish hwb_s09_b92554ae:

    # Marina "Nope, I’m not tired anymore, so I’ll just read some more."
    Marina "Неа, я больше не чувствую усталости, поэтому просто еще почитаю."

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:370
translate spanish hwb_s09_60aac9e1:

    # Amber "Alright. Good night."
    Amber "Хорошо. Спокойной ночи."

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:372
translate spanish hwb_s09_090d9677:

    # Marina "Night night!"
    Marina "Спокойной!"

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:376
translate spanish hwb_s09_3e91e1f4:

    # "I leave her up in the front as I head back to my bed and fall into it."
    "La dejo adelante mientras regreso a mi cama y me dejo caer en ella."

# game/script/hwb_s09.rpy:378
translate spanish hwb_s09_d7dfe427:

    # "After bunching up my blankets around me, it doesn’t take long to fall asleep."
    "Después de arremolinar mis cobijas a mi alrededor, no tardo en quedarme dormida."

